le-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great plugin-The BEST support!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrelas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrelas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bearsmaggie\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0946494575f008cc3dde124d839f8285?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0946494575f008cc3dde124d839f8285?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bearsmaggie\" class=\"reviewer-name\">bearsmaggie</a> em <span class=\"review-date\">outubro 23, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I’m not a programmer and guilty of clicking on something wondering what it will do only to have contact support for help to undo! I can’t remember a time I have received such thorough, complete and understandable support. I would recommend this plugin just to experience the support if you need them, but on its own, the plugin is great too. I have three areas on the home page I attend to that I am able to have clients read testimonials. One of my favorites is the slider at the bottom of the page that gives a sampling of testimonials and offers the option to read more just by clicking the link. Very-very impressive!! THANK YOU SUPPORT FOR BEING THERE FOR ME!! </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n		